  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Tibial tray fixation FEA credibility assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for finite element analysis (FEA) prediction of primary fixation stability of a cementless tibial tray under physiological loading during total knee arthroplasty (TKA). COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case micromotion conditions for a Class II orthopedic implant at Model Risk Level 3. Full 13-factor assessment: all factors either assessed (meeting required levels) or formally scoped-out with documented rationale.",
